Nathaniel Marston https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nathaniel_Marston 0 Nathaniel Marston (July 9, 1975 – November 11, 2015) was an American actor and producer. He is known for his two roles on ABC's One Life to Live as Al Holden and Dr. Michael McBain from 2001 to 2007.
